1. *Porodični* izleti su nam omiljeni vikend provod. (Family outings are our favorite weekend activity.)
2. Ovo je *porodična* kuća koja se već generacijama nasleđuje u mojoj porodici. (This is a family house that has been inherited in my family for generations.)
3. Oni su proveli *porodične* praznike na moru. (They spent family holidays at the seaside.)
4. *Porodični* odnosi su nam jako važni. (Family relationships are very important to us.)
5. Moj prijatelj radi u *porodičnom* preduzeću. (My friend works at a family-owned company.)
6. Ovo je *porodično* naselje u kojem većina ljudi poznaje jedni druge. (This is a family-friendly community where most people know each other.)
7. *Porodični* lekar nam je savetovao da vodimo zdraviji način života. (Our family doctor advised us to lead a healthier lifestyle.)
8. Oni su nedavno usvojili *porodično* dete. (They recently adopted a child into their family.)
9. U našem *porodičnom* albumu ima mnogo lepih uspomena. (Our family album contains many beautiful memories.)
10. *Porodična* tradicija je da se svake godine okupimo kod bake na Badnje veče. (It's a family tradition to gather at our grandma's house on Christmas Eve.)